On Sat, 2006-06-24 at 19:37 +0200, Stefan Richter wrote:
> 
> -               if (down_trylock(&video->sem)) {
> +               if (mutex_trylock(&video->mtx)) {
this is a bug!
mutex_trylock follows the spinlock trylock convention, not the semaphore
trylock convention!!!
